<text top="48" left="41" width="1020" height="54" font="1">One evolution of Social Media - Crowd Sourcing</text>
<text top="155" left="58" width="876" height="40" font="2">Crowd sourcing simply means using the effort of many </text>
<text top="198" left="58" width="108" height="40" font="2">people</text>
<text top="241" left="58" width="497" height="40" font="2">• Many hands make light work</text>
<text top="284" left="58" width="555" height="40" font="2">• The wisdom of crowds theory….</text>
<text top="328" left="58" width="902" height="40" font="2">• Applied to complex problems conventional computing </text>
<text top="371" left="98" width="202" height="40" font="2">cannot solve</text>
<text top="457" left="58" width="929" height="40" font="2">Also applied outside the realm of strict computing with the </text>
<text top="500" left="58" width="571" height="40" font="2">creation of crowd funding platforms </text>
</page>
